title: MaliceInstaller.exe
description:
Instead of boring you with a long paragraph, I'm just going to make a list.

- Rainbow Crystal Weapon Skins.
- EXP Rate is not a set value, it changes through out the game to smooth out your leveling experience.
- Referral system like no other. Click Here!
- Unique Item Mall. Click Here!
- Fun and helpful staff who are very active.
- Recolored Leviathan Weapon, and Leviathan himself.
- Custom raid bosses ready once we finish preparing for the cap raise.
- More custom content coming to the server all the time.
- Downtime is kept to as little as possible.
- Our CBT will not result in a wipe, so you have no worries, we might just go down for a few hours for final release.
- Custom drop/money system, collect Crystals and sell them to an NPC for money.
- Custom NPC prices, which are lower than other servers.
- Item Merchant Pey has cash shop items for pretty cheap including t1-5 enhancement stones and bundles.
- Custom towns, a story explaining the changes will be here soon: "Link not Available yet."
- All Jewelry give an HP and SP bonus depending on rarity. (i.e. Whites = 100 HP/SP, Greens = 250 HP/SP etc.)
- Very Unique game interface for a newer game experience.
- Always coming up with newer and better ideas to bring to the server!
- Listen to player suggestions and bug reports.

This is a Fiesta Private Server, we have no affiliation with Gamigo or OnOnSoft.
